  <section class="strip3" id="how">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="strip3__grid">
        <!-- HOW IT WORKS -->
        <div class="strip3__cell">
          <div class="strip3__title">HOW IT WORKS</div>
         <p class="strip3__lead">
  Sponsorship is structured through Caelverum.<br />
  You are not expected to source or negotiate brand agreements independently.<br />
  We:
</p>
          <ul class="strip3__list">
            <li>vet participants</li>
            <li>structure sponsorship Components</li>
            <li>align brand partnerships</li>
            <li>define activation standards</li>
            <li>manage contracts and payments</li>
            <li>oversee reporting and delivery</li>
          </ul>

          <p class="strip3__muted">
            You focus on your work.<br />
            We manage the bridge.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- WHAT PRO-ACTIVE MEANS -->
        <div class="strip3__cell">
          <div class="strip3__title">WHAT “PRO-ACTIVE” MEANS</div>
        <p class="strip3__lead">
  Pro-active describes behaviour.<br />
  An attitude. A particular headspace.<br />
  It means:
</p>
          <ul class="strip3__list strip3__list--ticks">
            <li>internally directed</li>
            <li>self-accountable</li>
            <li>consistent without supervision</li>
            <li>dependable</li>
            <li>action is your currency</li>
            <li>willing to step up for those who support you</li>
            <li>capable of operating within defined agreements</li>
          </ul>

        </div>

        <!-- WHAT SUPPORT LOOKS LIKE -->
        <div class="strip3__cell">
          <div class="strip3__title">WHAT SUPPORT LOOKS LIKE</div>
          <p class="strip3__lead">
  Support is allocated in defined Components.<br />
  Examples may include:
</p>
          <ul class="strip3__list">
            <li>gym or training membership</li>
            <li>competition or event entry</li>
            <li>travel and accommodation</li>
            <li>production costs</li>
            <li>content development support</li>
          </ul>

          <p class="strip3__muted">
            Each Component carries agreed activation expectations.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

